Text: "I just finished my bag and took an uber to the airport.\n\nAfter three hours\
  \ waiting, I finally took the plane to Portugal. Once I arrived, I needed to find\
  \ a taxi to go to the hotel.\n\nIt was an amazing building, with a beautiful architecture.\
  \ As it was already late, I went to sleep, to charge \u201Cbatteries\u201D and be\
  \ readyfor next day adventures... to be continued..."
